    "# Import library esensial yang dibahas\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\n",
    "\n",
    "# Setup matplotlib agar grafik tampil di dalam notebook\n",
    "%matplotlib inline"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 🟢 Chapter 1: Introduction\n",
    "\n",
    "Pada bab pertama, buku ini mengenalkan konsep dasar *Machine Learning*, perbedaan antara *Supervised* dan *Unsupervised Learning*. Fokus utama praktik di bab ini adalah membangun model **klasifikasi pertama** menggunakan algoritma **k-Nearest Neighbors (k-NN)** pada dataset Bunga Iris.\n",
    "\n",
    "### 1.1 Memuat Dataset Iris\n",
    "Dataset Iris adalah dataset klasik di ML yang berisi ukuran kelopak (petal) dan mahkota (sepal) dari tiga spesies bunga Iris."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from sklearn.datasets import load_iris\n",
    "iris_dataset = load_iris()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"Kunci dari iris_dataset: \\n\", iris_dataset.keys())\n",
    "print(\"\\nNama target (spesies): \", iris_dataset['target_names'])\n",
    "print(\"Nama fitur: \", iris_dataset['feature_names'])"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 1.2 Memisahkan Data (Train & Test Split) dan Melatih Model (k-NN)\n",
    "Kita perlu memisahkan data menjadi data latih (*training set*) dan data uji (*test set*)."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from sklearn.neighbors import KNeighborsClassifier\n",
    "\n",
    "# Memisahkan data (75% latih, 25% uji)\n",
    "X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(\n",
    "    iris_dataset['data'], iris_dataset['target'], random_state=0)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Inisialisasi model k-NN dengan k=1\n",
    "knn = KNeighborsClassifier(n_neighbors=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Melatih model\n",
    "knn.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Mengevaluasi model\n",
    "akurasi = knn.score(X_test, y_test)\n",
    "print(f\"Akurasi model k-NN pada test set: {akurasi:.2f} (atau {akurasi*100:.0f}%)\")"
   ]
  },
